Who: Kandin Firepot<br>
Hand him the note from Arintir<br>
<br>
say<br>
&quot;Hail, Kandin&quot;<br>
&quot;What Oil?&quot;<br>
<br>
Kandin will give you a 'Sproket' now time to go to<br>
<br>
Zone: Plane of Fear<br>
Who: Broken Golem<br>
<br>
hand the broken golem the spoket to spawn<br>
<br>
Who: Enraged Golem<br>
Objective: Green Oil<br>
Level 65, 150k HPs, doubles for 400 and hits slow, slowable, Hand of Ro will debuff, 3 groups 55+<br>
<br>
